{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1801, "height": 2467, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "说一二言，益书日读一二本，游浮度日枉做人。富贵骄淫难长享，贫而勤俭必不贫。忠厚一分一分福，耕稼一年一年谷。宝惜米谷记荒年，精打细算惜银钱。为人好花老来知差，为人好赌终日自苦。傲不可长，欲不可纵，志不可满，乐不可极；业莫若敬，居莫若俭，行莫若让，事莫若勤。\n", "block_bbox": [181, 217, 1513, 443], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "勤劳治家之本，和顺齐家之本，谨慎保家之本，诗书起家之本，忠厚传家之本。欲足福禄速读书，不读诗书子孙愚。贤肖子孙勤耕读，好从耕读下功夫。", "block_bbox": [183, 462, 1511, 565], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "—广东紫金县蓝塘杜氏家训", "block_bbox": [261, 586, 767, 624], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "谚云：治国容易治家难，能治家者必立族长，家政先从族长而治也，夫何难哉？所云族长，在前如夏传子，以长之其理甚当，但恐无接踵之贤，其何如乎？余谓尧曾让舜，舜亦让禹，治国尚且让贤，况乎治家乎？由此观之，凡吾一脉流传者，不拘长少，惟贤能者居之。若子孙中有不法不肖之徒，以法治之，使其勿乱家规族范。勉之勉之，勿负吾之望矣。\n", "block_bbox": [182, 645, 1513, 934], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "《杜氏家法序》（杜国楷）", "block_bbox": [263, 954, 767, 995], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "遵祖述以启后人，笃宗亲以光前代，守父命以谨百行。", "block_bbox": [263, 1014, 1153, 1057], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "—《杜氏三纲》", "block_bbox": [263, 1077, 543, 1118], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "鸣里居以纪坐落，详籍贯以固根基，志庐墓以传山水，开园地以守创垂，和母党以联姻眷，陈父族以振家声，胪妻男以敦伦纪，列子姓以亲诸姑。", "block_bbox": [184, 1137, 1512, 1241], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "—《杜氏八条》", "block_bbox": [265, 1263, 544, 1303], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "孝弟为先，耕读为本，宗族宜睦，纲常宜正，酒色勿贪，崇正黜邪，赌博宜禁，安分守法，劳动为生，早完赋税。\n", "block_bbox": [185, 1322, 1512, 1429], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "—《杜氏十训》", "block_bbox": [267, 1450, 546, 1492], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "忠孝吾家之宝，经史吾家之田。", "block_bbox": [267, 1513, 788, 1556], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "——宋·尚书杜孟的治家格言", "block_bbox": [267, 1578, 753, 1617], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "劝君莫惜金缕衣，劝君惜取少年时。花开堪折直须折，莫待无花空折枝。", "block_bbox": [267, 1637, 1399, 1681], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "——唐代杜秋娘之《金缕衣》，这是一首脍炙人口的诗作，它教育了一代又一代的中华儿女好好珍惜少年的时光，努力学习，不悔一生。", "block_bbox": [190, 1701, 1513, 1807], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "吾之妊身，在乎正顺。及其生也，思存于抚爱。其长之也，威仪以先后之，礼貌以左右之，恭敬以监临之，勤恪以劝之，孝顺以内之，忠信以发之，是以皆成而无不善。汝曹庶几勿忘吾法也。\n", "block_bbox": [185, 1827, 1516, 1996], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "—《华阳国志》载：南郑人郑宣妻杜泰姬撰《诫诸女及妇书》，是告诫女儿和媳妇教育孩子的一封书信。她针对不同的教育内容建议采取不同的教育方式和方法，以便取得良好的教育效果。她认为，长者应为孩子的表率，通过长者的言行举止去感化、熏陶、规劝孩子，使其在耳濡目染中逐渐形成良好的观念、品质", "block_bbox": [185, 2016, 1516, 2242], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1620, 649, 1691, 1270], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 18}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三五四", "block_bbox": [1631, 1859, 1675, 1965], "block_id": 18, "block_order": 19}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9158000946044922, "coordinate": [181.7476806640625, 217.16513061523438, 1513.6563720703125, 443.4580383300781]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9109015464782715, "coordinate": [185.34124755859375, 2016.1502685546875, 1516.351806640625, 2242.4951171875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9066458344459534, "coordinate": [182.16571044921875, 645.02685546875, 1513.4306640625, 934.524169921875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.893595278263092, "coordinate": [185.8223876953125, 1827.370849609375, 1516.4111328125, 1996.920166015625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8534034490585327, "coordinate": [185.8348388671875, 1322.0447998046875, 1512.3336181640625, 1429.7418212890625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8469117283821106, "coordinate": [184.33966064453125, 1137.1893310546875, 1512.223388671875, 1241.3221435546875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8378443121910095, "coordinate": [183.03790283203125, 462.7538757324219, 1511.2724609375, 565.56591796875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.837523877620697, "coordinate": [190.09210205078125, 1701.23583984375, 1513.640869140625, 1807.0615234375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7212560772895813, "coordinate": [267.45721435546875, 1637.2060546875, 1399.72607421875, 1681.169921875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6782054305076599, "coordinate": [263.588623046875, 1014.4036865234375, 1153.690673828125, 1057.7928466796875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6543173789978027, "coordinate": [267.7922058105469, 1513.3173828125, 788.109130859375, 1556.0625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6381258964538574, "coordinate": [263.07537841796875, 954.20654296875, 767.0364379882812, 995.566162109375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.617887020111084, "coordinate": [267.3818359375, 1450.8345947265625, 546.6259155273438, 1492.3709716796875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6061190962791443, "coordinate": [267.8162841796875, 1578.612548828125, 753.25927734375, 1617.515380859375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5912012457847595, "coordinate": [265.5655517578125, 1263.440673828125, 544.6080322265625, 1303.086669921875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5723704695701599, "coordinate": [261.91577